# CampusPass — Implementation Plan

A college event management and ticketing platform (Eventbrite-style for Indian colleges) with 3 user roles, Razorpay payments, and QR-code ticketing.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Razorpay Keys**: You'll need to provide Razorpay test-mode `key_id` and `key_secret` in `.env`. The app will work in test mode without real payments.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **MongoDB**: You'll need a MongoDB Atlas connection string (or local MongoDB). The `.env.example` will document all required variables.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Cloudinary**: For image uploads, Cloudinary credentials are needed. Alternatively, the app will fall back to local file storage using `multer`.

---

## Architecture Overview

```
campuspass/
├── backend/          # Express.js API server
│   ├── config/       # DB connection, cloudinary config
│   ├── controllers/  # Route handlers
│   ├── middleware/    # Auth, error handling, validation
│   ├── models/       # Mongoose schemas
│   ├── routes/       # API routes
│   ├── utils/        # Helpers (QR gen, email, etc.)
│   └── server.js     # Entry point
├── frontend/         # React + Vite
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── api/      # API client (axios)
│   │   ├── components/  # Reusable UI components
│   │   ├── contexts/ # Auth context
│   │   ├── pages/    # Route pages
│   │   └── lib/      # Utilities
│   └── ...
└── README.md
```

---

## Proposed Changes

### Backend — Express.js + MongoDB

#### [NEW] backend/package.json
Express server with dependencies: `express`, `mongoose`, `bcryptjs`, `jsonwebtoken`, `cors`, `dotenv`, `multer`, `cloudinary`, `razorpay`, `qrcode`, `express-validator`, `nodemailer`.

#### [NEW] backend/server.js
Entry point — connects to MongoDB, mounts routes, starts server on port 5000.

#### [NEW] backend/config/db.js
MongoDB connection using Mongoose with `MONGO_URI` from env.

#### [NEW] backend/config/cloudinary.js
Cloudinary configuration for image uploads (optional, graceful fallback).

#### [NEW] backend/models/User.js
Schema: `name`, `email`, `password` (hashed), `role` (student/organizer/admin), `college`, `phone`, `referralCode`, `referredBy`, `createdAt`.

#### [NEW] backend/models/Event.js
Schema: `title`, `description`, `category` (Tech/Fest/Music/Sports), `college`, `date`, `venue`, `price`, `totalTickets`, `ticketsSold`, `image`, `organizer` (ref User), `status` (pending/approved/rejected), `featured`, `coupons[]`, `createdAt`.

#### [NEW] backend/models/Booking.js
Schema: `event` (ref), `user` (ref), `ticketId` (unique), `qrCode` (data URL), `status` (confirmed/cancelled/checked-in), `payment` (ref), `createdAt`.

#### [NEW] backend/models/Payment.js
Schema: `booking` (ref), `user` (ref), `razorpayOrderId`, `razorpayPaymentId`, `razorpaySignature`, `amount`, `status` (pending/success/failed), `createdAt`.

#### [NEW] backend/middleware/auth.js
JWT verification middleware + role-based access control (`protect`, `authorize(...roles)`).

#### [NEW] backend/middleware/errorHandler.js
Centralized error handling middleware.

#### [NEW] backend/routes/auth.js & backend/controllers/authController.js
- `POST /api/auth/register` — signup with role
- `POST /api/auth/login` — login, return JWT
- `GET /api/auth/me` — get current user

#### [NEW] backend/routes/events.js & backend/controllers/eventController.js
- `GET /api/events` — list (with filters: category, college, date, search)
- `GET /api/events/:id` — single event
- `POST /api/events` — create (organizer only)
- `PUT /api/events/:id` — update (organizer/owner)
- `DELETE /api/events/:id` — delete (organizer/owner or admin)

#### [NEW] backend/routes/bookings.js & backend/controllers/bookingController.js
- `POST /api/bookings` — book ticket (generates QR code, prevents duplicates)
- `GET /api/bookings/my` — user's bookings
- `GET /api/bookings/event/:eventId` — event's bookings (organizer)
- `POST /api/bookings/verify/:ticketId` — verify/scan QR (organizer check-in)

#### [NEW] backend/routes/payments.js & backend/controllers/paymentController.js
- `POST /api/payments/create-order` — create Razorpay order
- `POST /api/payments/verify` — verify payment signature & confirm booking

#### [NEW] backend/routes/admin.js & backend/controllers/adminController.js
- `GET /api/admin/dashboard` — stats overview
- `GET /api/admin/events` — all events
- `PUT /api/admin/events/:id/approve` — approve/reject
- `PUT /api/admin/events/:id/feature` — toggle featured
- `GET /api/admin/users` — all users
- `GET /api/admin/transactions` — all transactions

#### [NEW] backend/utils/generateQR.js
QR code generation using `qrcode` package.

#### [NEW] backend/utils/sendEmail.js
Email notifications using `nodemailer` (booking confirmations).

#### [NEW] backend/.env.example
Template with all required env variables.

