#### [NEW] frontend/src/pages/Events.jsx
Event listing with filters (category, college, date, search).

#### [NEW] frontend/src/pages/EventDetails.jsx
Full event details, booking button, Razorpay payment flow.

#### [NEW] frontend/src/pages/StudentDashboard.jsx
Booking history, downloadable QR tickets.

#### [NEW] frontend/src/pages/OrganizerDashboard.jsx
